OL,4,Cfail to hit new healthy eating targets
OL,6,FSupermarkets could be fined if they do
OL,7,Fnot sell healthier food, under a new
OL,8,FGovernment plan to tackle obesity.
OL,10,FThe "healthy food standard" will apply
OL,11,Fto retailers and manufacturers in
OL,12,FEngland as part of a 10-year strategy
OL,13,Fto cut diet-related diseases, the
OL,14,FDepartment of Health and Social Care
OL,15,F(DHSC) said.
