OL,3,CSupermarkets could be fined if they
OL,4,Cfail to hit new healthy eating targets
OL,6,FInitially developed by innovation
OL,7,Fagency Nesta, the policy introduces
OL,8,Fmandatory health targets for retailers
OL,9,Fwhile giving them flexibility in how
OL,10,Fto meet them, such as by tweaking
OL,11,Frecipes, running price promotions on
OL,12,Fhealthier items, or redesigning store
OL,13,Flayouts.
OL,15,FSupermarkets will be required to
OL,16,Freport sales data and those that fail
OL,17,Fto hit targets could face financial
OL,18,Fpenalties, Nesta suggested.
