OL,3,CSupermarkets could be fined if they
OL,4,Cfail to hit new healthy eating targets
OL,6,FNesta analysed 36 million supermarket
OL,7,Ftransactions, finding an average
OL,8,Fshopping basket health score of 67 out
OL,9,Fof 100, and has set a target to raise
OL,10,Fthis to 69.
OL,12,FIts modelling shows that raising the
OL,13,Fscore by just two points would cut
OL,14,Fobesity by around a fifth over three
OL,15,Fyears, helping more than three million
OL,16,Fpeople to achieve a healthier weight.
