OL,6,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting said:
OL,7,F"If everyone who is overweight reduced
OL,8,Ftheir calorie intake by around 200
OL,9,Fcalories a day ` the equivalent of a
OL,10,Fbottle of fizzy drink ` obesity would
OL,11,Fbe halved.
OL,13,F"This Government's ambition for kids
OL,14,Ftoday is for them to be part of the
OL,15,Fhealthiest generation of children
OL,16,Fever. That is within our grasp. With
OL,17,Fthe smart steps we're taking today, we
OL,18,Fcan give every child a healthy start
OL,19,Fto life.
