OL,6,F"Our brilliant supermarkets already do
OL,7,Fso much work for our communities and
OL,8,Fare trying to make their stores
OL,9,Fhealthier, and we want to work with
OL,10,Fthem and other businesses to create a
OL,11,Flevel playing field.
OL,13,F"Through our new healthy food
OL,14,Fstandard, we will make the healthy
OL,15,Fchoice the easy choice, because
OL,16,Fprevention is better than cure."
OL,18,FThe Government aims to introduce
OL,19,Fmandatory reporting by the end of this
OL,20,Fparliament in 2029, with the standard
OL,21,Fto be achieved some way into the next.
