OL,6,FKen Murphy, chief executive of Tesco,
OL,7,Fwelcomed the announcement, while Simon
OL,8,FRoberts, chief executive of
OL,9,FSainsbury's, called it an "important
OL,10,Fand positive step forward in helping
OL,11,Fthe nation to eat well".
OL,13,FKatharine Jenner, director of the
OL,14,FObesity Health Alliance, said: "This
OL,15,Fis a fair and evidence-based
OL,16,Fprescription for better health; big
OL,17,Fbusinesses urgently need the
OL,18,Fgovernment to level the playing field
OL,19,Fto help them focus on selling products
OL,20,Fthat help people live well."
