OL,6,FEnvironment Secretary Steve Reed said:
OL,7,F"Our food strategy will bring together
OL,8,Fthe health plan, food producers and
OL,9,Fretailers to make sure we can feed the
OL,10,Fnation more healthily while growing
OL,11,Fthe economic success of our food
OL,12,Fsector."
OL,14,FAnna Taylor, executive director of the
OL,15,FFood Foundation, said: "The
OL,16,Fintroduction of mandatory reporting by
OL,17,Fall large food companies, including
OL,18,Ftakeaway chains, on the healthiness of
OL,19,Ftheir food sales is a game changer."
